          "text": "Open door to life and peace,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Window into glory."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "All who seek Him, soon are found,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Made His close relation:"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Christ our pathway, Christ our home,"
        },
